Cam::

She lay in the CR chamber and frowned. She felt more like she was 
being grounded. She wanted to play with the new bot. Run with another 
canine bot. Like she used to with her family. She couldn't help but 
whimper and whine a bit, thinking of her mom and dad. The repairs 
were complete, yet she stayed inside.  A whimpering noise could be 
heard from outside the chamber.
